## Status and next steps

| Component | Status |
|-----------|--------|
| Theoretical framework | Complete (ARC v5.0 preprint) |
| Kuznetsov Basis | Defined, partially validated |
| Empirical support (Acomys/Mus RNA-seq) | Partial — 5 genes confirmed |
| PREDICTED genes (piezo1/2, yap1, kcnq1-5) | Require patch-clamp, AFM, ATAC-seq |
| Combined protocol test | Not yet conducted |
| Minimal falsifiable experiment | Defined, ready for lab execution |

**The experiment that would move this from framework to finding:**
Adult mouse digit-tip amputation.
Three groups: V_mem alone / V_mem + soft matrix + immune permission / vehicle.
Primary endpoint: regeneration score (µCT, day 42).
Expected result if ARC-3 correct: group 2 > group 1 by >4×.

